schools.name: Palm Bay Magnet Senior High School

data.description: Welcome to your cozy new 2-bedroom, 2 ½ bathroom townhouse in Palm Bay, FL! This two-story beauty is all about comfort and style. Think newly updated primary bathroom (yes, it's as nice as it sounds), and a 2021 water heater for those never-cold showers. Upstairs, there are not one, but two owner's suites - talk about a win!  And yes, it's pet-friendly - bring your two pups (up to 40 lbs)!The community pool? Right across the parking lot. Talk about convenience! Plus, the HOA's got your back, covering water, sewer, and trash. No more pesky bills! You're right in the action here, with shops and restaurants a hop away. Beach day? You're just 13 minutes from sandy toes and ocean waves. And don't forget the luxury vinyl flooring - it's everywhere and it's awesome. Come see for yourself!
